ALL DIRECTORY -- Routines for memory allocation and deallocation.
----------------------------------------------------------------

Files compiled into Zoltan:

mem_const.h        -- Prototypes for memory allocation and deallocation
                      routines in mem.c.  Definition of LB_MALLOC.

mem.c              -- Memory allocation routines LB_array_alloc and LB_malloc.
                      Memory deallocation routine LB_free.
		      Parameter setting routing LB_Set_Malloc_Param.

all_allo_const.h   -- Prototypes for Zoltan-specific memory allocation and 
                      deallocation routines in all_allo.c.  

all_allo.c         -- Zoltan-specific Memory routines LB_Special_Malloc and
                      LB_Special_Free.
		      Parameter setting routing LB_Set_Malloc_Param.

free_structure.c   -- Calls method-specific routines to free any persistent
		      data structure when changing methods or freeing LB object.
